        "generatedLyrics": "[Intro]\n\n[Verse]\nSunlight streams through the glass panes\nDust motes dance in golden lanes\nFingers trace the polished wood\nWhere melodies are understood\n\n[Pre-Chorus]\nA gentle hum begins to rise\nReflecting skies within my eyes\nA simple chord, a tender sigh\nAs passing moments drift on by\n\n[Chorus]\nOh, the strings begin to sing\nWhat sweet emotions they can bring\nA whispered tale, a gentle art\nFrom deep within my beating heart\n\n[Post-Chorus]\nClassical grace, a timeless sound\nWhere peace and beauty can be found\n\n[Break]\n\n[Verse]\nEach note a pearl, precisely placed\nA delicate and measured haste\nFrom nimble touch, the music flows\nAs summer breeze through garden grows\n\n[Pre-Chorus]\nA quietude, a soft refrain\nTo wash away all earthly pain\nA tapestry of sound so pure\nThat time itself cannot obscure\n\n[Chorus]\nOh, the strings begin to sing\nWhat sweet emotions they can bring\nA whispered tale, a gentle art\nFrom deep within my beating heart\n\n[Bridge]\nThe melody starts to ascend\nA story that will never end\nA moment held, a breath so deep\nSecrets that the wood does keep\n\n[Verse]\nA arpeggio, a sweet cascade\nIn shadowed alcoves, unafraid\nThe resonance, a soft embrace\nLeaving not a single trace\n\n[Chorus]\nOh, the strings begin to sing\nWhat sweet emotions they can bring\nA whispered tale, a gentle art\nFrom deep within my beating heart\n\n[Post-Chorus]\nClassical grace, a timeless sound\nWhere peace and beauty can be found\n\n[Outro]",
